headline: Business people: James Lawrence to chair Metropolitan Airports Commission board
summary: AIRPORTS The Metropolitan Airports Commission announced that Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz has appointed James Lawrence as chair of the MAC board, which oversees Minneapolis-St. Paul International Airport and six general aviation airports in the Twin Cities, effective Wednesday. Lawrence previously chaired the commission’s Planning, Development and Environment Committee and was acting vice chair of ...
